{"tid":813542,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"係唔係每個女仔group都一齊幻想過姑婆屋","createTime":"2018-09-10T13:45:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-11T08:55:35.000Z","uid":4176,"like":65,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0e4383d79814d2ff2c72fb530b2441ceb9910741","tid":813542,"uid":4176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T13:45:05.000Z","msg":"唔知係唔係因爲以前去完啲畢業定新生camp<br />\n以前同小學中學同學都有一齊幻想過將來大家一齊住係間姑婆屋<br />\n大家會互相照顧 夜晚又會一齊傾心事<br />\n有時仲會一齊去ikea睇傢私<br />\n呦下邊個style會靚啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同住hall係唔同feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但大個之後先發現根本無可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我好掛住以前大家一齊幻想嘅時光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ad8564288301cb3dc088dc397477a38ae77cf38","tid":813542,"uid":1255,"like":75,"dislike":7,"score":68,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T13:46:13.000Z","msg":"係得豬閪先會圍喂餵咁諗<br />\n靚既又點會諗埋呢D無謂野<br />\n一早去拍晒拖啦"},{"pid":"a58a34dc8e35f3bf2f842b2b667cca5ca6fb80da","tid":813542,"uid":208364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T13:46:42.000Z","msg":"無喎"},{"pid":"d684cb3038a61c9ca02e82510b8c9b4ae4b23ea5","tid":813542,"uid":208364,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"7ad8564288301cb3dc088dc397477a38ae77cf38","tid":813542,"uid":1255,"like":75,"dislike":7,"score":68,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T13:46:13.000Z","msg":"係得豬閪先會圍喂餵咁諗<br />\n靚既又點會諗埋呢D無謂野<br />\n一早去拍晒拖啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T13:47:33.000Z","msg":"咪係，同朋友傾緊大家男朋友買咩樓好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6d34beae16f95cac89ab6063ac3fa6a8dbbb870","tid":813542,"uid":4176,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7ad8564288301cb3dc088dc397477a38ae77cf38","tid":813542,"uid":1255,"like":75,"dislike":7,"score":68,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T13:46:13.00